  "Description": {
    "English": "An exclusive <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Multi-Tool</span>.<br><br>This unusual ceremonial staff was hand-forged by a Korvax Priest Entity in tribute to the Atlas.<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">Take</span> this Multi-Tool to add it to your collection, or <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Exchange</span> it with your current Multi-Tool. Swap between active Multi-Tools from the Utilities section of the Quick Menu (<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>).",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一台专属<span class=\"name name-stellar\">多用途工具</span>。<br><br>这柄献给阿特拉斯的独特仪式权杖是由一名科尔瓦克斯神父实体亲手打造而成。<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">收下</span>这个多用途工具，将它加入你的收藏，或与你现在的多用途工具<span class=\"name name-stellar\">交换</span>。在快捷菜单（<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>）中的工具部分切换可用的多用途工具。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "一個獨特的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">工具組</span>。<br><br>這款不尋常的儀式手杖，由科瓦族牧師存在體手工打造，用以敬奉寰宇。<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">取走</span>這個工具組加入你的收藏，或是與目前工具組<span class=\"name name-stellar\">交換</span>。利用快捷選單 (<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>) 的機能頁面切換使用中的工具組。"
  },
